org.apache.flex.swf.tags

Class ProductInfoTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.Tag
      • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.ProductInfoTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IManagedTag, ITag

    public class ProductInfoTag
extends Tag
implements IManagedTag
    Represents a ProductInfo tag in a SWF file.

    This represents a ProductInfo SWF tag. It is used to embed information about the product, which was used to construct the SWF, including it's edition, major version, minor version, and build number, and the date the SWF was constructed.
